t.com/news/report.php/id/120783|title=Melbourne to host the Australian F1 Grand Prix until at least 2023|date=12 September 2015|work=[[Autosport|autosport.com]]|accessdate=12 May 2018|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823031340/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120783|archive-date=23 August 2016|url-access=limited}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Azerbaijan Grand Prix]]\n|{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Baku City Circuit]], [[Baku]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|url=http://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/society/2491434.html|title=Azerbaijan signs 10-year-contract for holding Formula-1|date=8 February 2016|work=Trend|accessdate=12 May 2018|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162322/https://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/society/2491434.html|archive-date=12 June 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Bahrain Grand Prix]]\n|{{Flagicon|BHR}} [[Bahrain International Circuit]], [[Sakhir]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=https://www.racefans.net/2018/04/25/ecclestone-parting-shot-liberty-f1-calendar-headache/|title=How Ecclestone's parting shot to Liberty added to their F1 calendar woes|last1=Rencken|first1=Dieter|date=25 April 2018|website=RaceFans|accessdate=20 May 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[British Grand Prix]]\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Silverstone Circuit]], [[Silverstone]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/formula1/48933290|title=British Grand Prix: New Silverstone deal announced until 2024|date=10 July 2019|website=[[BBC Sport]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711020056/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/formula1/48933290|archive-date=11 July 2019|accessdate=11 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Canadian Grand Prix]]\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Circuit Gilles Villeneuve]], [[Montr\u00e9al]]\n|align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|last1=Keating|first1=Steve|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/motor-racing-prix-montreal/motor-racing-canadian-gp-organisers-announce-10-year-extension-idINL4N0OO00C20140607|tit